Are you wondering to do this week as the curfew period prevents you from leaving your house? Well, Radio Africa Group audiences will be able to catch the good vibes and the exclusive rave experience starting this Saturday. The two-hour live performance will be on Kiss TV and FM as well as Homeboyz radio social media platforms from 5pm to 7pm. The performance will be hosted by the giant presenters 'Raverend' Shaffie Weru and Kamene Goro. On the decks will be Dj Hypnotic and Dj Kym NickDee. During the three-hour programme, the beauty and darkness of Nairobi life and the world will be discussed. The hosts will wine and dine as they entertain you during this coronavirus period.